snippet.title: JUMPY BUNNY | TEASER DEMO
snippet.description:
Obey the carrots and accept the challenging levels with a silly Bunny! Jump, jump, and jump. This game is about jumping with precision and determination.

Play it: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2946700/JUMPY_BUNNY/
